      value: "I think this is it. I\u2019ve finally found the castle the source of
        whatever has been tormenting this town.  The air here feels\u2026 wrong.
        Heavy. Like something is watching.  There\u2019s a skeleton by the bonfire.
        It\u2019s moving. Alive, somehow. I didn\u2019t think things could get any
        stranger, but this place keeps proving me wrong."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7530094599482637185, guid: 9537804b5f94dc349b019fcf42d3ca2e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: playerController
